另一位网友问道：“为什么这是 TikTok 有史以来最好的入口[？]”</p><p>克拉维茨在上述电视采访中告诉法伦，他“无法逃脱”有关他的大围巾的病毒迷因，这些围巾经常被编辑以使配饰看起来更大。</p><p> “我住在巴哈马......我习惯了炎热的天气，我不得不去商店。我当时正在买一些杂货，我想戴上一条小围巾来保护我的喉咙，这就是我的围巾，”他回忆道。</p><p>法伦回应说，该物品更像是“一条毯子”。</p><p>克拉维茨补充道：“不过，这就是互联网的问题，这就是问题所在——围巾变得越来越大。”</p><p>上周五（9 月 22 日）克拉维茨在内华达州拉斯维加斯举行的 2023 年 iHeartRadio 音乐节上进行了表演。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lenny-kravitz-joins-tiktok-with-giant-viral-scarf-3503679">兰尼·克拉维茨 (Lenny Kravitz) 戴着巨型围巾加入 TikTok 的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 Epic Games Store 上的《全面战争：法老》推迟至“2024 年初” https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/total-war-pharaoh-delayed-to-early-2024-on-epic-games-store-3503671?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=total-war- 《法老王》延迟至 2024 年初在 Epic-games-store 上发售Imogen DonovanMon, 25 Sep 2023 11:23:20 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsPC https://www.nme.com/?p=3503671 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/total-war-pharaoh-delayed-to-2024-epic-games.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/total-war-pharaoh-delayed-to-2024-epic-games.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/total-war-pharaoh-delayed-to-2024-epic-games-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/total-war-pharaoh-delayed-to-2024-epic-games-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/total-war-pharaoh-delayed-to-2024-epic-games-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/total-war-pharaoh-delayed-to-2024-epic-games-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/total-war-pharaoh-delayed-to-2024-epic-games-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>游戏在 Steam 和 Mac 上的发布不受影响</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/total-war-pharaoh-delayed-to-early-2024-on-epic-games-store-3503671">Epic Games Store 上推迟至“2024 年初”发布的《全面战争：法老》</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/total-war-pharaoh-delayed-to-2024-epic-games.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/total-war-pharaoh-delayed-to-2024-epic-games.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/total-war-pharaoh-delayed-to-2024-epic-games-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/total-war-pharaoh-delayed-to-2024-epic-games-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/total-war-pharaoh-delayed-to-2024-epic-games-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/total-war-pharaoh-delayed-to-2024-epic-games-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/total-war-pharaoh-delayed-to-2024-epic-games-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>即将推出的策略游戏<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/total-war-pharaoh"><em>《全面战争：法老》</em></a>不得不将其在<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/epic-games">Epic Games</a> Store 的发布时间推迟到“2024 年初”， <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/creative-assembly">Creative Assembly</a>表示它和粉丝们一样“失望”。</p><ul><li><strong>了解更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/best-strategy-games-3199564">2023 年最佳策略游戏</a></strong></li></ul><p>这是为了在游戏中引入“额外的社交功能”，团队将需要更灵活的时间框架来实现这些功能。</p><p>粉丝们意识到他们通过 Epic Games Store 预订的<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/total-war">《全面战争</a>：法老》</em>已被退款，这表明 Creative Assembly 正在进行某种更新。</p><p> “我们向所有计划受此消息影响的粉丝致歉。要知道，我们也很失望，否则我们期待明年初欢迎您来到古埃及，” <em>《全面战争</em>》官方 X 帐户上的<a href="https://twitter.com/totalwar/status/1705213415726211255" target="_blank" rel="noopener">帖子</a>继续说道。 </p><figure id="attachment_3497357" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3497357" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3497357" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Total-War-Pharaoh-court.jpg" alt="全面战争：法老。图片来源：创意大会。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Total-War-Pharaoh-court.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Total-War-Pharaoh-court-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Total-War-Pharaoh-court-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Total-War-Pharaoh-court-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Total-War-Pharaoh-court-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Total-War-Pharaoh-court-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3497357" class="wp-caption-text">全面战争：法老。图片来源：创意大会。</figcaption></figure><p>该游戏在<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/steam">Steam</a>和 Mac 上的发布不受影响， <em>《全面战争：法老》</em>将于 10 月 11 日上市。不过在此之前，对于在 Steam 上预购该游戏的玩家来说，有一个独家抢先体验期。</p><p> 9 月 29 日至 10 月 2 日期间，玩家将能够对抗两个派系——拉美西斯（埃及）和伊尔苏（迦南）。另外还有胡夫和阿肯那顿埃及古代遗产以及图达利亚和穆瓦塔利赫梯古代遗产。</p><p>所有战斗机制以及自定义战斗都将提供，最多 60 个回合可多次重玩。尽管如此，在线多人游戏并不包括在内。</p><p>虽然<em>《全面战争：战锤》的</em>奇幻背景从世界各地的民间传说和宗教中汲取了无数灵感，但历史上的<em>《全面战争》</em>游戏却没有那么奢侈。 </p><figure id="attachment_3497356" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3497356" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3497356" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Total-War-Pharaoh-2.jpg" alt="全面战争：法老。图片来源：创意大会。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Total-War-Pharaoh-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Total-War-Pharaoh-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Total-War-Pharaoh-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Total-War-Pharaoh-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Total-War-Pharaoh-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Total-War-Pharaoh-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3497356" class="wp-caption-text">全面战争：法老。图片来源：创意大会。</figcaption></figure><p> “我们首先追求的是历史真实性，这意味着我们不会试图准确地再现当时发生的事件，”导演托多尔·尼科洛夫<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/total-war-pharaoh-director-talks-the-challenge-of-not-having-dragons-3497336">在接受<em>NME</em>采访时</a>解释道。</p><p>此外， <em>《全面战争：法老》</em>将受到战斗中天气和天气变化以及地形的影响，地形会响应降雨以应对反应性战斗挑战。 “我们正在尝试通过使用不同的功能来解决可能被认为是单位多样性较差的问题，以便提供整体的选择多样性，”他推测道。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/starbreeze">Starbreeze</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/payday-3-developer-apologises-for-nightmare-server-issues-at-launch-3503549">回应了<em>《收获日 3》</em>服务器出现大规模问题的报道</a>，这些问题导致玩家无法在游戏发布周末进入游戏。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/total-war-pharaoh-delayed-to-early-2024-on-epic-games-store-3503671">Epic Games Store 上推迟至“2024 年初”发布的《全面战争：法老》</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
