 Unity 在“听证会担忧”后对有争议的运行时间费用进行了更改https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/unity-makes-changes-to-controversial-runtime-fees-after-hearing-concerns-3503635?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=unity-makes-changes-听证会后有争议的运行时间费用问题Imogen DonovanMon, 25 Sep 2023 10:52:57 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsVideo Game Culture https://www.nme.com/?p=3503635 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-open-letter-to-customers-and-runtime-changes.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-open-letter-to-customers-and-runtime-changes.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-open-letter-to-customers-and-runtime-changes-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-open-letter-to-customers-and-runtime-changes-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-open-letter-to-customers-and-runtime-changes-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-open-letter-to-customers-and-runtime-changes-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-open-letter-to-customers-and-runtime-changes-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>使用 Unity Personal 或 Plus 制作的游戏不会产生任何费用</p><p>在“听证会问题”首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/unity-makes-changes-to-controversial-runtime-fees-after-hearing-concerns-3503635">之后，Unity 对有争议的运行费用进行了更改</a>。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-open-letter-to-customers-and-runtime-changes.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-open-letter-to-customers-and-runtime-changes.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-open-letter-to-customers-and-runtime-changes-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-open-letter-to-customers-and-runtime-changes-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-open-letter-to-customers-and-runtime-changes-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-open-letter-to-customers-and-runtime-changes-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-open-letter-to-customers-and-runtime-changes-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/unity">Unity</a> Create 总裁 Marc Whitten 为游戏引擎新运行时费用<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/unity-backlash-explained-why-game-developers-are-speaking-out-on-twitter-3497816">的疏忽致歉</a>，并宣布了将要实施的更改。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/british-racing-greats-a-charity-driven-celebration-of-car-culture-and-gaming-3469412">英国赛车伟人：慈善驱动的汽车文化和游戏庆典</a></strong></li></ul><p>“我想首先说：我很抱歉，”惠滕在<a href="https://blog.unity.com/news/open-letter-on-runtime-fee" target="_blank" rel="noopener">公司官方博客上发表的一篇文章</a>中说道。他表示，新的定价计划在公布之前缺乏反馈，下一步的任务是倾听客户的声音，再次恢复信任。</p><p> “正是你们让 Unity 变得伟大……我们已经听到了你们的担忧，我们正在对我们宣布的政策进行更改以解决这些问题，”Whitten 继续说道。</p><p>这些变化是 Unity Personal 或 Plus 计划中的用户不会受到运行时费用政策的影响。因此，仅包含 Unity Pro 和 Enterprise 上的内容。 </p><figure id="attachment_3497200" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3497200" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3497200" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-runtime-fee-debacle.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-runtime-fee-debacle.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-runtime-fee-debacle-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-runtime-fee-debacle-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-runtime-fee-debacle-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-runtime-fee-debacle-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-runtime-fee-debacle-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3497200" class="wp-caption-text"> Unity 徽标 图片来源：Unity Technologies</figcaption></figure><p>现有游戏的安装不会向创建者收费，新的定价计划仅对“使用 2024 年（或以后）发布的长期支持 (LTS) 版本创建或升级到的游戏生效”，目前称为 2023 LTS ”。</p><p>如果一款游戏满足这两个标准，那么一旦该产品的总收入超过 100 万美元以及“初始参与量”超过 100 万次，运行时费就会被激活。</p><p> “对于需要缴纳运行时费的游戏，我们可以让您选择 2.5% 的收入分成，或者根据每月参与游戏的新用户数量计算的金额，”Whitten 解释道。 “这两个数字都是根据您已有的数据自行报告的。您将永远被收取较少的金额。”</p><p>为了回应定价计划，Unity 收到了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/unity-received-death-threat-from-one-of-its-employees-claims-report-3498506">来自其一名员工的死亡威胁</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3497864" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3497864" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3497864" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-backlash-cult-of-the-lamb.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-backlash-cult-of-the-lamb.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-backlash-cult-of-the-lamb-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-backlash-cult-of-the-lamb-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-backlash-cult-of-the-lamb-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-backlash-cult-of-the-lamb-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-backlash-cult-of-the-lamb-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3497864" class="wp-caption-text"> 《Cult Of The Lamb》开发商 Massive Monster 公开反对 Unity 的定价变化 图片来源：Devolver Digital</figcaption></figure><p>出于安全考虑，旧金山警察局关闭了两个办公室后，旧金山警察局表示，“举报方通知[他们]，一名雇员使用社交媒体对其雇主发出威胁”。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中，英国竞争和市场管理局<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/microsoft-gets-one-step-closer-to-buying-call-of-duty-developer-activision-blizzard-3502676">暂时批准</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/microsoft">微软</a>收购<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/activision">动视暴雪</a>，理由是“剩余问题”。</p><p>在“听证会问题”首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/unity-makes-changes-to-controversial-runtime-fees-after-hearing-concerns-3503635">之后，Unity 对有争议的运行费用进行了更改</a>。</p> ;
